            h3 Here's How It works
            ul
              li Open to US and UK only
              li Start date: April 2nd / End date: April 6th
              li 500 $0.01 codes released each day at 12:00 PM PDT
              li $0.01 codes to be redeemed on Amazon US or Amazon UK
              li $0.01 codes apply to the white 3ft PowerLine Lightning only
              li $0.01 codes must be used prior to May 3rd
              li Complete the steps opposite to participate
          div.right
            div.one
              div 1. 
